postReview.title: Crystal Palace 1-2 Manchester United: Mount and Zirkzee strike in comeback victory
postReview.description: Mason Mount and Joshua Zirkzee scored in the space of nine second-half minutes as Manchester United rallied to beat Crystal Palace.

postReview.title: Crystal Palace 1-2 Manchester United: Mount y Zirkzee firman la remontada
postReview.description: Mason Mount y Joshua Zirkzee marcaron con nueve minutos de diferencia en la segunda parte y el Manchester United remontó ante el Crystal Palace.

postReview.title: Crystal Palace 1 x 2 Manchester United: Mount e Zirkzee marcam na virada
postReview.description: Mason Mount e Joshua Zirkzee marcaram no espaço de nove minutos do segundo tempo, e o Manchester United virou sobre o Crystal Palace.

postReview.title: Crystal Palace 1-2 Manchester United: Mount e Zirkzee firmano la rimonta
postReview.description: Mason Mount e Joshua Zirkzee a segno a distanza di nove minuti nella ripresa: il Manchester United rimonta e batte il Crystal Palace.

postReview.title: Crystal Palace 1-2 Manchester United : Mount et Zirkzee signent la remontée
postReview.description: Mason Mount et Joshua Zirkzee ont marqué à neuf minutes d'intervalle en seconde période pour permettre à Manchester United de renverser Crystal Palace.

postReview.title: Crystal Palace 1:2 Manchester United: Mount und Zirkzee treffen beim Comeback-Sieg
postReview.description: Mason Mount und Joshua Zirkzee trafen innerhalb von neun Minuten nach der Pause, Manchester United drehte die Partie bei Crystal Palace.

postReview.title: كريستال بالاس 1-2 مانشستر يونايتد: ماونت وزيركزي يسجّلان في فوز بقلب النتيجة
postReview.description: ماسون ماونت وجوشوا زيركزي يسجّلان بفارق تسع دقائق في الشوط الثاني ليقودا مانشستر يونايتد لقلب النتيجة على كريستال بالاس.

postReview.title: Crystal Palace 1-2 Manchester United: Mount e Zirkzee marcam na vitória de reviravolta
postReview.description: Mason Mount e Joshua Zirkzee marcaram no espaço de nove minutos na segunda parte, na reviravolta do Manchester United frente ao Crystal Palace.
